                    "description": "Lead Regional HRM/HRBP providing HR management for Benelux, Nordics, and Spain. Supporting the EMEA Service Delivery Operations organization (>750 staff members and UK as largest employee population). Supporting the VP Operations and Service Delivery (member of European Leadership Team) and the Operational Leadership Team. Partnering with ELT, regional and local leadership, and international HR to support client group activity in the form of improving organizational effectiveness, driving change and culture, and brokering HR services including HR projects, process execution, procedure development. With a focus on employee engagement, performance management and development and organisational development. Aligning HR management with the direction, priorities, and method of operation of the business and implementing HRM tools, projects, policies, programs and processes in support of those. Serving as a trusted advisor and influencer providing candid and unbiased counsel through an interactive partnership with the business.\nServing as the face of HR to the organisation and broker and influence services with HR Centres Of Excellence, as well as other HR functions and business units in the organisation. Providing end-to-end HR support and ensure that all business needs are met.Managing social relations including the entire consultation process with the Dutch Works council (OR), staff representatives, prevention officer and local management. Working closely with HR shared service delivery to ensure high level customer experience. Providing excellent HRM to management and employees.",
